Thief Nora: Let's go and rescue Cors-san quickly!
Explorer Armada: Haa! Don't underestimate explorers!

Mage Relm: I think they were researching how to tame

Explorer Armada: I may not be familiar with Fotizona, but I

Explorer Armada: W-What is this...? Is this also the

Mage Relm: This is the proof of our bond! The wings of the

Explorer Armada: If I'm with everyone, does that mean I can
use this magical power too?
Explorer Armada: Clea, can I come with you too?
Clea: Of course, let's fight together.

Cors the Wanderer: I wonder if it's about time... The
disturbance caused by the nobles and the Senate heading
towards the royal palace has come to an end.

Cors the Wanderer: The guild members are rough with people.
Now, let's evacuate to a safe place ahead of time--
Girl: Kyaa! Help me! Father, mother!
Cors the Wanderer: A child's voice...

Cors the Wanderer: No, no, no...! It's absolutely impossible
to save someone from a monster like that.

Cors the Wanderer: Besides, I have already fulfilled my
duty.

Cors the Wanderer: I absolutely won't let a child die.
Making troublesome promises is not my thing, you know...
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Clea: Ect...! Why are you here!?

Young explorer Ect: I-I thought I could fight too... For the
sake of Papa and everyone else...

Young explorer Ect: If you hear the voice of a dragon...?
Before I knew it, I was trembling here, scared...

Clea: Ect was originally in a support role, but I asked her
to come here because of my selfishness.
Clea: So please evacuate to a safe place, it'll be alright.
Young explorer Ect: But, if that's the case, then I...

Clea: I hate to say it so harshly, but it's not a situation
where we can fight while protecting Ect, who is running
away.

Clea: I used to be called a timid and scared little girl,
and I think that's still true to this day.

Clea: But, the journey so far and the encounters with my
companions have given me the courage to admit that I am a
timid and scared little girl.

Clea: Ect, what will you do? Will you run away from your own
cowardice, or will you stand and fight?

Young explorer Ect: I... I will stand and fight! If I run
away here, I won't be able to face Clea-san and Papa for the
rest of my life!

Young explorer Ect: That's why I'll go! I won't run away,
I'll go with you to the rooftop!
Clea: Thank you very much, it's reassuring.

Young explorer Ect: I'm scared, but I won't run away... I'll
protect the place Papa loved and my friends.
